      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with potential? This car is in poor condition and needs some dedicated TLC, but it offers a great foundation for anyone looking to restore a classic or use it for valuable parts! It's a budget-friendly opportunity for a hands-on owner to bring a vehicle back to life or secure rare components at a great price.",
